          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Tool results \u2014 API responses, database query output, file contents \u2014 can be arbitrarily large. Inserting them raw into the context without a size check will blow the tool budget in a single turn. Summarize results above a token threshold using a cheap fast model (Claude Haiku) before adding them to the message thread. Record that the result was summarized so the agent can request the full result if needed."
